  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide school supplies like school bags, notebooks, and stationery for 100 internally displaced economically disadvantaged primary school pupils whose education has been affected by the civil crisis that has plagued Cameroon English-speaking regions for four years now. The targeted pupils are those who have been able to relocate to Douala, one of the safe regions, and are currently going to school but face significant economic challenges and may likely drop out.</narrative>
  </description>
